FBIS4-39083 "drsov108_i_94001" FBIS-SOV-94-108 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 CENTRAL ASIA Kazakhstan World Bank Grants $15 Million Loan World Bank Grants $15 Million Loan LD0606090494 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network in Kazakh 0800 GMT 6 Jun 94 LD0606090494 Almaty Kazakh Radio Network Kazakh BFN [Text] The World Bank confirmed a $15.7 million loan to Kazakhstan. The loan will be used for modernizing the Republic's oil-recovery industry and to attract additional foreign investments in the industry. The loan will be paid back in 17 years.
